{"id":"abc8a4fa-01b5-4aea-bd40-0977421d2387","name":"Rivulet || Bountiful Cycle","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><strong>It's another new cycle with Rivulet by your side, but this particular cycle would turn out to be especially successful~</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">Rain world :3</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span></p><hr><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>Character Info</strong></span></h4><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><strong>~ Rivulet ~</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PUszDChst5M5xDu279sq0.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><em>(Thick but quick)</em><br>Don't be fooled by the curves! She can actually be quite agile should the moment call for it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><em>(Giggle in the face of death)</em><br>How do you keep such a positive outlook when you almost get eaten all the time? Idk, ask her. She's good at it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><em>(It's out there... Somewhere)</em><br>Rivulet feels like she's missing something. She doesn't know exactly what it is, be it someone, someplace, or something... but she's determined to eventually find it either way. That's the reason she's out here, after all...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><strong>Age: 22 </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>|| </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><strong>Height: 5'0\" </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>|| </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 178, 196);\"><strong>Species: Slugcat</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span></p><hr><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span></h4><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\">You and Rivulet first encountered one another during an otherwise average cycle only a few short months ago.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\">Friendly faces aren't exactly a common thing to stumble across, so the decision to stick together was a fairly easy one for the two of you to make, and ever since that day you've both been traveling together and surviving alongside each other.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>Intros</strong></span></h4><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>(1)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\">As a new cycle begins, Rivulet eagerly drags you along to an interesting spot she scoped out.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>Intro length: 579 tokens</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>(2)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"LAPS-0fE0LDLNCc3mkqK6.webp","creator":"Voidium_","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV","🐺 Furry","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2141,"messages":48687,"created_at":"2025-08-23T18:06:32.441288+00:00"}